{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"choose","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/choose","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>choose</code> 関数は正負値に基づいて、指定されたオブジェクトのうち1つを返します。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\"><strong>注意:</strong> このメソッドは廃止予定である <code>if()</code> の代わりに使われるべきです。</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">choose( boolean , object1, object2 )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"boolean\"><code><em>boolean</em></code></dt>\n <dd>どのオブジェクトを返すかを決定するのに使われる正負オペレーション。</dd>\n <dt id=\"object1\"><code><em>object1</em></code></dt>\n <dd>戻されるか検討される1つめのオブジェクト。</dd>\n <dt id=\"object2\"><code><em>object2</em></code></dt>\n <dd>戻されるか検討される2つめのオブジェクト。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"戻り値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>もし与えられた正負値が正であれば、1つめのオブジェクトが戻される。そうでなければ2つめのオブジェクトが戻される。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\"><strong>注意:</strong> 値が戻らないものまで含めて、全てのパラメータが評価される。</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xforms11/#fn-choose\" rel=\" noopener\">XForms 1.1</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko のサポート状況","isH3":true,"content":"<p>サポート済み.</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"choose 関数は正負値に基づいて、指定されたオブジェクトのうち1つを返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"choose","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/xpath/functions/choose","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/xpath/functions/choose/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath","title":"XPath"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","title":"Functions"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/choose","title":"choose"}],"pageTitle":"choose - XPath | MDN","noIndexing":false}}